   Japan's Barriers
   On Some Trades
   Appear to Ease
   ---
   Goldman, Salomon Cleared
   To Offer Securities Tied
   To Foreign Exchange
   ----
   By Clay Chandler and Marcus W. Brauchli
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
